## 1. Executive Voice vs. Internet Voice
**Source:** [Lewis Commercial Writing - Internet Voice](https://www.lewiscommercialwriting.com/post/internet-voice)

"Internet Voice" (clickbait) destroys B2B trust. Executive Voice is **philosophical, pragmatic, and challenging.**

* **Rule 1:** Write to a **specific smart peer**, not a general audience.
* **Rule 2:** Use **Substance**. Every post must contain a real story, a real metric, or a challenging principle.
* **The Filter:** "Would I say this exactly like this to a potential client over coffee?" If no, rewrite.

