## 2. Customer-Led Language Mining
**Source:** [LCW - Simplify Your B2B Message](https://www.lewiscommercialwriting.com/post/simplify-your-b2b-message)

Great copy is "assembled" from what customers say. Alexander Lewis explicitly cites **Reddit** as a key source.

* **Tactics:** Mine Reddit (e.g., r/Recruiting) and G2 reviews for:
    * **Anger Words:** What they hate about current hiring tools.
    * **Status Quo Workarounds:** The messy spreadsheets they use because tools fail them.
* *100Hires Application:* Build LinkedIn hooks using these exact phrases to signal instant empathy.

