## 3. The "Blended Ghostwriting" Workflow
**Source:** [LCW - Ghostwriting Secrets](https://www.lewiscommercialwriting.com/post/ghostwriting-secrets)

Founder-led marketing fails when it relies on the founder's "free time."

1.  **Extract:** A "Point Person" interviews the CEO for 30-45 minutes (Stories, objections, hot takes).
2.  **Mining:** Point Person mines the transcript for the "Executive Voice."
3.  **Drafting:** Point Person drafts 3-4 posts/week.
4.  **Polish:** CEO spends 10 mins tweaking nuance and approving.

